    "name": "Poolside",
    "profile": "Los Angeles based duo Filip Nikolic and Jeffrey Paradise are good friends who are inspired by California, mezcal, dancing, good food and wine. Their sound is called Daytime Disco. Filip is a Danish producer now living in LA who plays bass in Ima Robot; Jeffrey throws the infamous Blow Up party in San Francisco and was in the hardcore band The Calculators with Luke and Vito from the Rapture.\r\nNikolic left the project in 2017, now consisting solely of Jeffrey Paradise.",
